loops:

loops in java help us execute  a piece of code again and again until the codition is true.
to avoid redundancy in code. three are mainly 4 types of loops

why we should learn  about loop?
	because loops help us write cleaner and scalable code.for example if u have to check password feild on a webage you can create different variation of data in a excel sheet then you
	pick all the values ony by one and test the feild.
	
